Description:
**BY APPOINTMENT ONLY DURING THE ALLOCATED INSPECTION TIME. CONTACT AGENT TO ARRANGE** The Quay to Unlock the Perfect Lifestyle
From the lights of the City skyline, across the harbour, over Port Phillip Bay and towards magnificent sunsets behind the Bolte Bridge the views will simply amaze you.
Located in the Quays South tower residential complex, this fantastic 3 bedroom apartment on the 21st floor is a perfect place to call home.
Modern kitchen with white cabinetry provides ample storage and incorporates an island stone bench. Integrated stainless steel Miele appliances consisting of an oven with a gas stove top, provides the ideal set up for a budding chef.
Spacious open plan dining and living area with full-length floor to ceiling windows adjoins a west facing covered balcony, ideal for outdoor entertaining and setting up for a BBQ. The main bedroom consists of a study nook and Stylish fully tiled ensuite with its own private balcony. The 2nd bedroom with mirrored robes also has its own ensuite, whilst the 3rd bedroom with bir shares a central bathroom with European laundry.
Great features include
2 side by side car spaces
Split system reverse cycle heating and cooling
Floorboards in living, dining and bedroom areas
East and West Security entrances
Double glazed windows
NBN Internet ready
The complex sports full facilities which include an indoor pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium, cinema, study centre, Poker room, dining room, bike room, communal BBQ area with landscaped gardens, and a tennis court.
With the District Docklands Shopping complex nearby, shop to your heart's content, popcorn movie nights at the new Hoyts cinema or chill out at the O'Briens ice hockey/ skate rink.
Close proximity to the CBD, situated in the free tram zone and close to Southern Cross station. Easy access to the freeway and smooth travels to Melbourne airport.
Invest now move in later.

Description:
Sleek Elm & Stone 2-Bedroom Corner Apartment
This stunning new light-filled corner apartment in the sophisticated Elm & Stone complex was designed by award-winning architects DKO. A sleek interior features a generous living area, two balconies, harbour and city-edge views, two double bedrooms with BIRs, a bathroom and concealed laundry.
Complex designed by award-winning architects DKO
Cutting edge interior
Enjoy an ultra-convenient lifestyle
Sleek prestige Smeg & stone kitchen
Video intercom security
Split-system air conditioning
Secure basement parking
Exceptional owner occupier/investment potential
Low owners corporation fees
Amenities
The outstanding Elm & Stone complex offers tranquil surroundings with access to a landscaped garden with reflection pond, swimming pool, fully-equipped gym, rooftop deck and BBQ Facilities along with a library which includes multiple study and meeting areas.
Would you like to arrange a virtual tour of this property? Let our agents know and wed be happy to oblige!
Location
Enjoy a walk-to lifestyle from the heart of NewQuay and the ever improving features of the Docklands precinct including The District which features Hoyts Cinemas, Street hawker food outlets plus the soon to be opened fresh food complex The Market which will have butchers, delis, bakeries, coffee roasters, Woolworths supermarket and Dan Murphys. Other attractions include easy access to the Capital City Trail, Marvel Stadium, leading Universities, trams (free City Circle line), Southern Cross Station plus the Skybus to Melbourne Airport.
Please contact Lynn Lum on 0474 044 293 to arrange an exclusive inspection.

66m²

Description:
Spectacular Views From Docklands Finest Complex
Enjoy panoramic northern views from high up in the magnificent Marina Tower which offers state-of-the art facilities and a lifestyle embracing the benefits of both inner-city and waterfront living. Combining resort-style amenities with uninterrupted views this cutting-edg- apartment features two bedrooms, main with an ensuite plus a second fully-tiled bathroom and concealed laundry. A spacious living and dining area includes a sleek kitchen with stainless steel stove opening to a covered balcony ideal for enjoying the views and relaxing with friends.
Marina Tower The Docklands finest complex
Enjoy an ultra-convenient waterfront lifestyle
Video intercom security
Cutting edge interior
Sleek fully-equipped kitchen
Two R/C air conditioners (living & balcony)
Secure basement car space
Panoramic Victoria Harbor and City skyline views
The spectacular Marina Tower, arguably one of the finest developments in the Docklands precinct offering residents prestigious resort-style amenities, including access to a lobby lounge, library and meeting rooms. A private business centre, cinema, private dining room and kitchen, billiard room, a fully- equipped gym, rooftop lap-pool leading to an expansive deck with stunning views of Melbournes skyline.
Enjoy a walk-to lifestyle from the edge of NewQuay with the ever improving features of the Docklands precinct including The District which features Hoyts Cinemas, Street hawker food outlets plus the fresh food complex The Market with its many gourmet offerings, butchers, delis, bakeries, coffee roasters, Woolworths supermarket, Dan Murphys and NewQuay Park. Other attractions include easy access to the Bourke Street precinct including Docklands Park and Sports arena, Capital City Trail, Marvel Stadium, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, leading Universities, trams (free City Circle line), Southern Cross Station plus the Skybus to Melbourne Airport.

Description:
MARVEL IN DOCKLANDS
Dont miss out on this incredible apartment in the Docklands. Located on La Trobe Street where Docklands meets the CBD sits the Lacrosse Building, ideally located next to Marvel Stadium, public transport, restaurants and shopping.
With high returns in a sensation locale, this 2 bed, 2 bath apartment has fantastic views of the CBD, includes a modern kitchen with stone bench tops and dishwasher, mirrored built in robes in the bedrooms, and clean, contemporary finishes in the bathrooms.
A Euro-laundry, private balcony, split system heating/cooling, secure swipe/intercom entry, and secure car space round out this well designed apartment.
Typical of modern apartment living, residents enjoy the use of the heated outdoor pool and gymnasium.
With world class shopping and sporting events on your doorstep, this low maintenance investment is close to public transport and only minutes from City Link.
Don't miss this amazing opportunity.

Description:
A safe investment in prime location.. No Cladding Issues
The Dream:
Centrally located in Docklands, offering stunning views of Melbourne City skyline on one side and minutes walk to Waterfront on the other, this apartment fulfills to the ultimate city living dream for its tenants.
The Abode:
This is an amazing investment in an area well known for tenant demand. This two bedroom, two bathroom apartment offers generous space, quality fittings and tucked-in European Laundry. Spacious lounge room with heating & cooling, leads to a huge balcony. Kitchen with endless cupboard space, dishwasher, stone bench top and gas appliances.
The Basics:
* Security Entrance, Foyer, Intercom and Entrance hall
* Open Plan living area looking over large balcony
* Modern kitchen with gas cooking, stainless steel appliances and dishwasher
* 2 bedrooms both with built in robes
* Split system heating/cooling
* Modern bathroom along with second bathroom off master
* Huge balcony with stunning views of the city
* Modern facilities including outdoor heated pool and large Gym.
The Locale:
Walk to Marvel Stadium, Southern Cross station precinct and Docklands Waterfront. Hop on to a free tram at door step to the City, stroll to Harbour Town Shopping centre or explore the dining options with endless cafes & restaurants, all within minutes reach. All at your door step
Next Steps:
Call, reach out, email but be quick as this is in high demand. Book an appointment!

53sqm (approx.) North-facing One Bedroom Apartment to Invest or Nest!
A stunning combination of low-maintenance luxury, designer style and light-filled space, this striking 1 bedroom apartment sets a high standard for market entry excellence. Investors will appreciate the value, first homebuyers can purchase with confidence, and those looking for a city base will be impressed by the lock-and-leave certainty. The central Docklands location sells itself with Newquay restaurants, Marvel Stadium, The District shopping, free city trams, and Southern Cross Station all nearby.
North-facing spacious open-plan living and dining
Stylish stainless steel appliance with plenty of storage space

Description:
A home near the water
Situated in the stunning Flinders Wharf complex, this 2 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom apartment is ideally suited for any astute first home buyers or savvy investor. Both spacious bedrooms offer built in robes and have direct access to the bathroom/en-suite, a serviceable kitchen with white stone bench tops, smeg stainless steel oven, gas cook top, microwave and dishwasher adjoining a spacious living area with access to a North facing balcony providing loads of natural light and a view of Docklands.
Features include central heating and cooling, security video intercom, a powder room/ laundry, a concierge, 24/7 security, indoor pool, spa, sauna, steam room and gym for your enjoyment.
Enjoy the best of both worlds in Flinders Wharf with this location so close to everything the Docklands, Southbank and CBD has to offer. You're near South Wharf Promenade which has an abundance of terrific bars and restaurants as well as DFO shopping, while you're also close to Batman Park, Crown Casino, Southbank Promenade restaurants including Merrywell and Il Pomodoro, riverside restaurants, trams on Spencer Street and Southern Cross Station.

A WONDERFUL MONTAGE

Description:
The Perfect Docklands Lifestyle Base!
Perched on the 8th floor of the stylish Lacrosse building, this stunning apartment has everything you need!
Offering a vibrant blend of contemporary city charm and elegance, this 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment is an opportunity not to be missed! Centrally located in Docklands only meters to Marvel Stadium, Southern Cross Station (30min to the airport), Melbourne CBD, cafes, restaurants, shops and attractions, this well designed residence is perfect for astute owner occupiers and savvy investors.
This classy corner apartment shows off amazing wrap-around views, perfect for entertaining and NYE fireworks overlooking Victoria Harbour. A generous, bright, and relaxed lounge/dining area with ample dining space flowing effortlessly to the open-plan living boasting an adjoining kitchen with modern stainless steel appliances. The spacious master bedroom comprises a large en-suite bathroom, double mirrored built-in robe and study nook, perfect for a study desk or reading. The second bedroom which also has access to their own separate bathroom and laundry, also comes with double mirrored built in robes providing ample storage for the low maintenance inner city living lifestyle.
The building facilities include a large outdoor pool and deck with a gym. This property also comes with a secure car space, reverse cycle heating/cooling in the living zone, along with intercom entry for added security.

Description:
Breathtaking harbour and bay views from this Palladio stunner!
Wake up with these spectacular Victoria Harbour and Port Phillip Bay vistas from this generous and stylish two bedroom, two bathroom apartment. Located on the 20th floor of the Palladio complex, youll get to enjoy all the modern creature comforts as well as a NewQuay precinct location youll love.
This is the highest floor where you can purchase this specific apartment layout in the Palladio building with these magnificent views!
Large undercover balcony the best vantage point to soak in the harbour and bay views, while you also get glimpses of the mountain ranges and Melbourne Star
Observation Wheel
Spacious central living and dining zone with access out to the balcony
Deluxe kitchen complete with s/steel Smeg and Bosch appliances
Both bedrooms with BIRs enjoy the harbour and bay vistas
Master bedroom features a stylish ensuite with unique circular shower
2nd bedroom with its own private balcony
Central bathroom, European laundry
Brand new carpet and freshly painted
Reverse cycle heating and cooling, additional wall heating
Secure intercom entry
Secure undercover car space
Designed by renowned Fender Katsalidis, The Palladio complex allows residents access to an exclusive health club featuring rooftop pool, private function area, vegetable garden and fully-equipped gym with stunning views.
The fantastic NewQuay precinct is just moments to Marvel Stadium, Capital City Trail, harbourside restaurants, nearby trams including the free City Circle line, Southern Cross Station, and the airport Skybus. Youre also near The District Docklands with fantastic shops, Hoyts Cinemas, 8 Street hawker food outlets, Woolworths supermarket, Dan Murphys, and the Market Lane fresh food precinct with butchers, delis, bakeries, and coffee roasters. The CBD is also so close where you have the best in Melbourne at your fingertips.

93m²

Description:
Penthouse Style Waterside Sanctuary on Victoria Harbour
When award winning architects Bates Smart designed Marina Home 22 in the prestigious Convesso building uppermost in their mind was a waterside sanctuary with an exceptional outlook above mast height overlooking the delightful Victoria Harbour.
Elegance, luxury and convenience above a vibrant promenade, a retreat escaping from the rigours of the city. Space and tranquillity are the themes flowing through this outstanding waterfront home.
A private entry flows through to large open living, spacious dining area and huge entertainer kitchen with butler's pantry and enough bench space to cater for a grand dinner party,
The master suite opens out onto the extensive balcony and features a large dressing room, loads of robe space and gleaming ensuite with separate shower and bath. Roomy second and third bedrooms with ample built-ins take advantage of the delightful northerly views. Both have direct access to the balcony. Well equipped laundry, double lock-up garage with remote entry, storage cage, secure entry with intercom.
Convesso boasts an incredible array of resident amenities including 25m swimming pool, gymnasium, residents lounge, business centre and boardroom. Great connectivity to the free tram zone, Southern Cross Station, Marvel Stadium, Dock Library, Buluk Park, Southern Star Wheel, District Docklands shopping and cinema.

Description:
Enjoy Stunning City & Victoria Harbour Views
This stylish apartment is located on the ninth floor of the widely acclaimed and popular Boyd Tower, in the heart of the NewQuay precinct. Boasting a superb backdrop with views spanning the City skyline and Victoria Harbour. The light-filled, spacious interior features a generous living and dining room flowing to a balcony and incorporating a full kitchen with high quality S/S appliances and wide bench. Complemented by 2-bedrooms, large main with study area, WIR, ensuite and a second balcony. Plus a pristine central bathroom, Euro laundry and car space.
Two balconies with City & Victoria Harbour views
Stylish stainless steel kitchen
Generous main bedroom with ensuite and balcony
Pristine central bathroom plus a European laundry
Reverse cycle heating and cooling
Additional wall heaters
Secure intercom entry
One car space
The facilities enjoyed by the residents of The Boyd Tower include a fully-equipped gymnasium, outdoor pool and open-air entertainment area with brilliant views perfect for relaxing with friends.
Situated right in the heart of the NewQuay precinct where there is so much to enjoy - with its brilliant access to the vibrant food and entertainment hub that is The District Docklands. Including the Hoyts Cinema and The Melbourne Star Wheel at your doorstep plus a wonderful array of waterside restaurants to dine in at night or the weekends; Marvel Stadium for footy fans or the Capital City Bike Trail. Accessibility to the rest of Melbournes inner-city amenities and transport hub is taken care of thanks to nearby free trams, Southern Cross Station, and the Skybus service to Melbourne Airport.
To arrange an exclusive viewing, please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304.

46sqm Terrace the Perfect Entertainer!
Situated in The Quays which is one of the most sought-after complexes in the NewQuay precinct, this modern 1 bedroom apartment delivers expansive alfresco entertaining and a striking waterside position so close to the CBD.
Perfect for owner-occupiers and investors

Description:
This Light Filled Oversize Residence in Dock 5 is Great Value
***This property is available for inspection by appointment - Please contact us to arrange a suitable time***
The first impressions of this delightful Dock 5 residence are the magnificent natural light flooding through the floor to ceiling windows and the spacious living area. Combine a strong sense of privacy and security and this John Wardle creation makes an inviting offering.
A private entry sweeps past the entertainer kitchen featuring loads of bench space, top of the range Bosch oven, dishwasher and roomy walk-in pantry. The expansive living and dining area features full length windows throughout and opens onto a wide balcony suitable for entertaining.
The master suite boasts a prominent view of Victoria Harbour and the Bolte Bridge to take in the famous Docklands sunsets. An oversize shower sets off a gleaming ensuite. A good sized second bedroom comfortably fits a queen size bed and tables.
A secluded main bathroom has the popular bonus of shower and separate bath, the laundry is also totally separate. The residence is fully air-conditioned and heated. Secure parking. Storage cage. Wine cellar.
Dock 5 boasts a stunning pool/gym/outdoor area, has secure intercom access, is a very well maintained building and provides easy access to Victoria Harbour waterfront, Dock Library, Free Tram stop and a full range of shopping, medical and personal services.
*** COVID-19 Announcement ***
If you're attending a Private Appointment, we request that you only attend if you are fit and healthy to do so and not under any self-isolation conditions. We request that you maintain a healthy distance from our team members, and if requested wait outside until the property is ready for the appointment. Lastly, please refrain from touching items/fixtures and doors within the properties. If you would like to view something in particular, please request the agent's assistance. Thank you.
